semester, academic, and annual permit prices begin prorating approximately 10 days after the first day of classes. the prorated amount ranges from $5 to $18 per week, depending on the type of permit. all semester, academic, and annual permits are refundable anytime prior to the last month of the permit's expiration date. the refund amount is calculated based on the prorated price of the permit, on the date the refund request is submitted, less a $10 processing fee.to request a permit refund, complete the permit refund request docusign form.